ns2:eventGroup.name: WIFI
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when performing WIFI mobility

ns2:eventGroup.name: SESSION_ESTABLISHMENT_EVALUATION
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when the operator suspect session establishment problems. The included events shall give enough information to confirm this suspicion and if a problem exist give an understanding on where in the 'system' the problem exists.

ns2:eventGroup.name: CCTR
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This Continuous Cell Trace scanner group shall include events that shall be possible have enabled 'all the time' (in other words shall not load the 'system' too much). The scanner contents shall give a general overview of the behavior in the eNB and able to indicate problems in the eNB.

ns2:eventGroup.name: INTERNAL
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: All other internal, non-periodic events, not ASN.1 encoded. UE, Cell or RBS level.

ns2:eventGroup.name: INTERNAL_PERIODIC
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: Outgoing events sent at regular periodic intervals. Not ASN.1 encoded. UE, Cell or RBS level. [Excluding the PM_INITIATED_UE_MEASUREMENTS sub-group]

ns2:eventGroup.name: GENERAL_EVALUATION
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined groups shall be used if a problem exists but the operator is unclear on where the problem is. The group shall include events that shows to the operator what kind of problem that exists in the eNB (HO, dropped sessions, or session establishment).

ns2:eventGroup.name: DROPPED_SESSION_EVALUATION
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when the operator suspect dropped call problems. The group shall contain events which give enough information to confirm this suspicion and if a problem exist give an understanding on where in the 'system' the problem exists.

ns2:eventGroup.name: MBMS
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when performing MBMS

ns2:eventGroup.name: RDT
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when performing Remote Drive Testing

ns2:eventGroup.name: MDT
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when performing MDT

ns2:eventGroup.name: CAPACITY_MANAGEMENT_EVALUATION
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when the operator would like to get an overview on the used capacity within the eNB.

ns2:eventGroup.name: SESSION_PERFORMANCE_EVALUATION
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when the operator would like to get an overview on the performance of the sessions within the eNB.

ns2:eventGroup.name: HANDOVER_EVALUATION
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group shall be used when the operator suspect handover problems. It shall include events which give enough information to confirm this suspicion and if a problem exist give an understanding on where in the 'system' the problem exists.

ns2:eventGroup.name: UETR_ONLY
ns2:eventGroup.ns2:desc: This predefined group indicates events that are only possible to use in UE Trace (UETR)
